trans-unit.source: Provides access to add attributes for one specific type to one specific <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable" />.
trans-unit.target: Fornece acesso para adicionar atributos para um tipo específico para um <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable" /> específico.

trans-unit.source: The first time an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> is queried for attributes for a type, if the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> was populated using <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> for that type, the delegate is passed a <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder>.
trans-unit.target: Na primeira vez que um <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> é consultada para atributos de um tipo, se o <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> foi preenchido usando <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> para o tipo, o representante é passado um <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> removes the callback reference and adds any attribute information provided by calls to <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> remove a referência de retorno de chamada e adiciona informações de atributo fornecidas por chamadas para <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Adds the contents of the provided attributes to the attribute table that created this builder.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o conteúdo dos atributos fornecidos à tabela de atributos que criou este construtor.

trans-unit.source: If an attribute conflicts with another attribute already included in the table, the last attribute added replaces previous attributes.
trans-unit.target: Se um atributo está em conflito com outro atributo já incluído na tabela, o último atributo adicionado substitui atributos anteriores.

trans-unit.source: Attributes can be added only to the type specified by <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Atributos podem ser adicionados somente para o tipo especificado pelo <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The attributes that are added to the table.
trans-unit.target: Os atributos que são adicionados à tabela.
